&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/4239&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/4239&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-6214&quot; title=&quot;Using standby replicas with an in memory state store causes Streams to crash&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-6214&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-6214&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: enable use of in-memory store for standby tasks&lt;/p&gt;

